<package>
	<id>com.peterdev.livefish</id>
	<name>LiveFish</name>
	<version>1.2</version>
	<compatibility>
		<firmware>
			<miniOS>11.0</miniOS>
		</firmware>
	</compatibility>
	<dependencies>
		<package>3D Touch Devices, iOS 11 - 11.4b3, mobilesubstrate</package>
	</dependencies>
	<descriptionlist>
		<description><![CDATA[
		iOS 11에서 사라졌던 6종의 물고기 라이브 포토를 불러옵니다.<br/>
		설정 -> 배경화면 -> 배경화면 선택 -> Live에 있습니다.<br/>
		사용해주셔서 감사합니다.<br/>
		자세한 사용법은 스크린샷을 봐주세요.]]>
	</description>
	<description><![CDATA[
		Bring back Live Fish Wallpapers to iOS 11 devices<br/>
		Go to Setting -> Wallpaper -> Choose a New Wallpaper -> Live<br/>
		Thank you for using this tweak
		]]>
		</description>
	</descriptionlist>
	<screenshots>
		<screenshot>
			<description><![CDATA[라이브 배경화면에 6종의 물고기를 추가시켜줍니다.
		    There are 6 Live Fish Wallpapers in the setting.app.
			]]>
			</description>
			<image>pic0.jpg</image>
		</screenshot>
	</screenshots>
	<changelog>
		<change>
			Added Depiction
		</change>
	</changelog>
